result.name: Kam Kee Cafe

reviews.text: Taste is so so,  not worth to try again but the decoration is quiet HK transitional style.

It does not seem like a good working place for wait staff as everyone of the servers were under stress. If you enjoy rude services or no services, then this will be the place for you. It serves only average food. But that terrible service is something.
Great milk tea, nice staff and good choice of breakfast.
Friendly Waiter with Good Hong Kong Style Food. Small seats and packed
HK style food, good quality with reasonable price. That is traditional HK food so visitor should try it.

reviews.text:
早餐首選☺
快😋正
食品價格雖然好似略貴，但品質高，而且裝修及擺設很不錯————比起這餐廳在觀塘  APM 的分店好很多！

雪糕紅荳冰$3O。
杯身窄長，真係飲得不爽。
職員服務態度很好 ，正想whatsapp他們的顧客服務給讚，晨早一份滿意的早餐，今天不錯啊！
